OpenStack,is,a,provider,of,various,open,source,project,components,that,facilitate,the,establishment,of,cloud,services,It,has,provided,standard,APIs,that,are,well,suited,for,multiple,implementations,The,OpenStack,Bare,Metal,API,is,a,RESTful,platform,for,interacting,with,the,cloud,provisioned,hardware,architecture,of,the,Bare,Metal,service,The,OpenStack,Bare,Metal,service,is,essentially,a,network,of,physical,servers,that,have,been,transformed,into,virtual,machines,and,made,available,to,service,providers,and,enterprises,through,the,cloud,infrastructure,Developers,can,use,the,OpenStack,Bare,Metal,API,AP,to,create,a,control,panel,through,which,users,can,acquire,privileged,rights,for,accessing,and,interacting,with,the,bare,metal,servers,in,the,cloud,environment